(base dmg * BS multiplier) + (bane/elemental * BS multiplier)<br>
or<br>
(base dmg + bane/elemental ) * BS multiplier<br>
<br>
i.e. The stake<br>
<br>
4 dmg BS + 12 dmg BS or 16 dmg BS?<br>
