<br>
So, I went and got a Johanius Stake of Slaying for myself. For those that don't know, the weapon is 4/21 with +12 vs vampyres. Fighting the coterie in Tenebrous Mountains (which are vampyres as far as I know), I never got a backstab higher than 82, my minimum for level 55. Looking over my logs, it also looks like my normal pierces were in the teens instead of around 50 as they are with my Ragebringer.<br>
<br>
First of all: are the coterie in Tenebrous really vampyres? If not, my test was incorrectly executed.<br>
<br>
If they are, my conclusion has to be that Bane damage still is not working for backstabs, and maybe is not working at all.<br>
