<br>
Ie with 15 damage poker, you get 50% higher backstabs than 10 damage poker (min damage disturbs this a bit tho).<br>
<br>
It is not exponential or whatever. Without backstab skill % raise, the 553 of level 60 max for 15 damage poker would effectively become 589 for 16 damage poker.<br>
